title: Morocco Central Bank Balance Sheet
description: Central Bank Balance Sheet in Morocco increased to 455645 MAD Million in September from 448538 MAD Million in August of 2022. Central Bank Balance Sheet in Morocco averaged 246208.29 MAD Million from 2001 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 455645 MAD Million in September of 2022 and a record low of 118725.88 MAD Million in January of 2002. This page provides - Morocco Central Bank Balance Sheet - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
